		<span style="color: #000000; font-size: medium;">﻿</span>
<p style="text-align: center;"><span style="color: #000000; font-size: x-large;"><strong>“冬之恋”——献给朋友们的歌</strong><strong> </strong></span></p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><span style="color: #000000; font-size: medium;">时间：<span style="font-family: Times New Roman;">2012</span>年<span style="font-family: Times New Roman;">12</span>月<span style="font-family: Times New Roman;">16</span>日晚<span style="font-family: Times New Roman;">19</span>：<span style="font-family: Times New Roman;">30</span></span></p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><span style="color: #000000; font-size: medium;">地点：民族音乐厅                         </span></p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><span style="color: #000000; font-size: medium;">主持人：王军（国家一级演员）  </span></p>
 
<p> <span style="font-family: Times New Roman; color: #000000; font-size: medium;"> </span></p>
<p><span style="color: #000000; font-size: medium;">一、女声独唱《阳光路上》<span style="font-family: Times New Roman;">                                                         </span>甲丁<span style="font-family: Times New Roman;"> </span>王晓岭词<span style="font-family: Times New Roman;">  </span>张宏光曲</span></p>
<p><span style="color: #000000; font-size: medium;">                        《美丽的心情》<span style="font-family: Times New Roman;">                                                              </span>张名河词  孟庆云曲</span></p>
<p><span style="color: #000000; font-size: medium;">                                                          演唱：李延心</span></p>
<p><span style="color: #000000; font-size: medium;">二、男高音独唱《和是我们共唱的歌》<span style="font-family: Times New Roman;">                                 </span>石顺义<span style="font-family: Times New Roman;"> </span>吴立生词<span style="font-family: Times New Roman;">  </span>王咏梅曲</span></p>
<p><span style="color: #000000; font-size: medium;"><span style="color: #000000; font-size: medium;">                            </span>《我的太阳》                      <span style="font-family: Times New Roman;">   [</span>意<span style="font-family: Times New Roman;">] Giovanni Capurro</span>词<span style="font-family: Times New Roman;"> Eduardo di Capua曲</span></span></p>
<p><span style="color: #000000; font-size: medium;">                                   演唱：张向华（文化部优秀剧目展演获奖者）</span></p>
<p><span style="color: #000000; font-size: medium;">三、笛子独奏《牧民新歌》<span style="font-family: Times New Roman;">                                                                       </span>王志伟<span style="font-family: Times New Roman;"> </span>简广易曲</span></p>
<p><span style="color: #000000; font-size: medium;">                                                  演奏：马芸（文华奖获奖者）</span></p>
<p><span style="color: #000000; font-size: medium;">四、男低音独唱《滚滚长江东逝水》<span style="font-family: Times New Roman;">                                    </span>电视剧《三国演义》主题曲</span></p>
<p><span style="color: #000000; font-size: medium;"><span style="color: #000000; font-size: medium;"><span style="color: #000000; font-size: medium;">                            </span></span>《我是中国人》<span style="font-family: Times New Roman;">                                                               </span>石飞词<span style="font-family: Times New Roman;"> </span>谷建芬曲</span></p>
<p><span style="color: #000000; font-size: medium;">                                                          演唱：赵健</span></p>
<p><span style="color: #000000; font-size: medium;">五、女声独唱《呼伦贝尔大草原》<span style="font-family: Times New Roman;">                                                       </span>克明词<span style="font-family: Times New Roman;"> </span>乌兰托嘎曲</span></p>
<p><span style="color: #000000; font-size: medium;"><span style="color: #000000; font-size: medium;">                        </span>《节日欢歌》                                     <span style="font-family: Times New Roman;">                                 </span>贺东久词 印青曲</span></p>
<p><span style="color: #000000; font-size: medium;">                                                          演唱：吴静</span></p>
<p><span style="color: #000000; font-size: medium;">六、二胡独奏《葡萄熟了》<span style="font-family: Times New Roman;">                                                                                        </span>周维曲</span></p>
<p><span style="color: #000000; font-size: medium;">                                            演奏：李晗<span style="font-family: Times New Roman;"> </span>（国内比赛多次获奖）</span></p>
<p><span style="color: #000000; font-size: medium;">七、女声独唱《和平年代》<span style="font-family: Times New Roman;">                                                                       </span>贺东久词 印青曲</span></p>
<p><span style="color: #000000; font-size: medium;"><span style="color: #000000; font-size: medium;">                        </span>《天路》<span style="font-family: Times New Roman;">                                                                                   </span>屈塬词<span style="font-family: Times New Roman;"> </span>印青曲</span></p>
<p><span style="color: #000000; font-size: medium;">                                      演唱：贾静思（第六届国际音乐节获奖者）</span></p>
<p><span style="color: #000000; font-size: medium;">八、琵琶独奏《十面埋伏》                                                  <span style="font-family: Times New Roman;">                                          </span>古曲</span></p>
<p><span style="color: #000000; font-size: medium;">                                     演奏：于源春（<span style="font-family: Times New Roman;">CCTV</span>民乐大赛金奖获得者）</span></p>
<p><span style="color: #000000; font-size: medium;">九、男声四重唱《弹起我心爱的土琵琶》<span style="font-family: Times New Roman;">                                </span>电影《铁道游击队》插曲</span></p>
<p><span style="color: #000000; font-size: medium;"><span style="color: #000000; font-size: medium;"><span style="color: #000000; font-size: medium;">                            </span></span>《少林、少林》<span style="font-family: Times New Roman;">                                                    </span>电影《少林寺》主题曲</span></p>
<p><span style="color: #000000; font-size: medium;">                                        演唱：张向华、肖笑、纪英明、赵健</span></p>
<p><span style="color: #000000; font-size: medium;">十、女高音独唱《芦花》<span style="font-family: Times New Roman;">                                                                           </span>贺东久词 印青曲</span></p>
<p><span style="color: #000000; font-size: medium;"><span style="color: #000000; font-size: medium;"><span style="color: #000000; font-size: medium;">                            </span></span>《苏三起解》<span style="font-family: Times New Roman;">                                                                        </span>根据京剧改编</span></p>
<p><span style="color: #000000; font-size: medium;">                           演唱：谢琳（国家一级演员、文化部优秀剧目展演获奖者）</span></p>
<p><span style="font-family: Times New Roman; color: #000000; font-size: medium;"> </span></p>
